item.title: Zombies will be all over Clarke Quay this Halloween
item.description: Source: Clarke Quay. Zombiefest for 2019. This Halloween, enter Clarke Quay at your own risk and prepare to become a zombie. From October 31st to November 2nd, Clarke Quay presents FOX The Walking Dead Halloween 2019, transforming the Singapore riverside into a zombie colony. Expect roaming walkers, themed decorations, games, and live music to thrill attendees. Clarke Quay’s FOX The Walking Dead Halloween celebrates the series’ highly anticipated October return.
